{"tid":1410670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"杯葛政府 由罷睇林鄭開始","createTime":"2019-08-05T02:13:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T02:13:51.000Z","uid":229886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c15d593b06665140b0225cb30d7b2d03cc333804","tid":1410670,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:13:51.000Z","msg":"成日話光復香港<br />\n首先要唔承認呢個政府<br />\n但次次林鄭出黎講野個個仆去睇<br />\n如果有次林鄭出黎講野<br />\n冇記者訪問 冇市民睇<br />\n我地有我地做<br />\n佢有佢對空氣講<br />\n咁就可以杯葛到政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}